<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Toque Mágico</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
}

body{
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fff,#ffe6f2);
    color:#d63384;
    overflow-x:hidden;
}

header{
    text-align:center;
    padding:40px 20px;
    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ffb6d9,#ffffff);
    box-shadow:0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,.1);
}

header h1{
    font-size:48px;
}

header p{
    font-size:18px;
    margin-top:10px;
}

.decoracao{
    font-size:35px;
    margin-top:15px;
}

.container{
    max-width:900px;
    margin:auto;
    padding:40px 20px;
}

.card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:30px;
    margin-bottom:30px;
    box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(255,105,180,.2);
    border:3px solid #ffc0cb;
}

.card h2{
    margin-bottom:15px;
    color:#ff1493;
}

.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    margin-top:15px;
    padding:15px 30px;
    background:#ff4fa3;
    color:white;
    text-decoration:none;
    border-radius:50px;
    font-size:18px;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#d63384;
    transform:scale(1.05);
}

footer{
    text-align:center;
    padding:25px;
    background:#ffd6eb;
    color:#c2185b;
    margin-top:30px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.flores{
    position:fixed;
    font-size:28px;
    opacity:.25;
}

.f1{top:20px;left:20px;}
.f2{top:100px;right:25px;}
.f3{bottom:30px;left:35px;}
.f4{bottom:80px;right:20px;}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="flores f1">🌸</div>
<div class="flores f2">🌷</div>
<div class="flores f3">🌺</div>
<div class="flores f4">💐</div>

<header>
    <h1>✨ Toque Mágico ✨</h1>
    <p>Transformando momentos com carinho e magia.</p>
    <div class="decoracao">
        🌸 🪔 🌷 💖 🌺
    </div>
</header>

<div class="container">

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📱 Opção 1 - WhatsApp</h2>
        <p>Fale conosco diretamente pelo WhatsApp.</p>

        <a class="btn"
        href="https://wa.me/5511943374143"
        target="_blank">
        Entrar em Contato
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h2>📞 Opção 2 - Ligar</h2>
        <p>Se preferir, faça uma ligação.</p>

        <a class="btn"
        href="tel:+5511943374143">
        Ligar Agora
        </a>
    </div>

</div>

<footer>
🌸 Toque Mágico • WhatsApp: +55 11 94337-4143 • 🪔 Feito com carinho 💖
</footer>

</body>
</html>
